":"want to display an annotation image instead.","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement this method to mark a point annotation with a view object. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method or have it return "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for that annotation, then implement"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instead."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" is an instance of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" (or equal to the map view’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property), return an instance of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(or a subclass thereof)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"text":"Related examples","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Add a